            <title><![CDATA[Voidwrought coming to PS5, Xbox Series in 2026]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/10/voidwrought-coming-to-ps5-xbox-series-in-2026</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/voidwrought-coming-to-ps5-xbox-series-in-2026.1319602/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Currently available for Switch and PC.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Kwalee [30 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/kwalee">Kwalee</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Powersnake [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/powersnake">Powersnake</a> will release <a title="Genres > Metroidvania [238 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/metroidvania">Metroidvania game</a> / <a title="Genres > Side-Scrolling [1,125 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/side-scrolling">side-scrolling</a> <a title="Genres > Action [3,117 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/action">action</a> <a title="Genres > Platformer [757 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/platformer">platformer</a> <em><a title="Games > Voidwrought [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/voidwrought">Voidwrought</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,573 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a> and <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,061 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a> in 2026, the companies announced. <span id="more-998416"></span></p><p>In addition to the digital release, physical standard and Collector’s editions distributed by <a title="Companies > Selecta Play [17 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/selecta-play">Selecta Play</a> will also be available for PlayStation 5 and Switch. The latter includes an outer box, soundtrack CD, three character magnets, one embroidered patch, and one metallic pin.</p><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Voidwrought-CE_10-08-25.jpg"></a></figure><p><em>Voidwrought</em> first launched for Switch and PC via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2014550/Voidwrought/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Steam</a> on October 24, 2024.</p><p>Here is an overview of the game, via its <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2014550/Voidwrought/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Steam page</a>:</p><blockquote><p><strong>About</strong></p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p>The coming of the Red Star heralds a new age. Emerging from its cocoon, the Simulacrum is driven to collect Ichor, the blood of the gods, from the monstrosities who hoard it.</p><p><em>Voidwrought</em> is a fast-paced 2D action platformer with tight traversal, varied abilities, and formidable boss battles. Find and equip powerful Artifacts to customize your playstyle. Excavate into the rubble of the Gray City to construct a shrine filled with loyal followers.</p><p><strong>Delve <a title="Games > Beneath [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/beneath">Beneath</a> the Surface</strong></p><p>Descend below the star-scorched surface and explore the multidimensional depths below. Witness the corrupted revelry of the Court, lose yourself in the icy tunnels of the Old Waters, and discover the grim fate of the Abandoned Expedition.</p><p>With sharp controls, engaging exploration, and deep lore to discover, Voidwrought is a dynamic addition to the modern Metroidvania genre.</p><p><strong>Unleash <a title="Companies > Ancient [8 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/ancient">Ancient</a> Artifacts</strong></p><p>The world is filled with treasures sought by the learned, the brave, and the mad. Scour the halls of your shrine, rend the corpses of defeated deities, and hunt in the hidden corners of the cosmos to find Artifacts capable of granting unique powers.</p><p>Discover and equip over 30 Artifacts, from spectral weapons to passive buffs, to match your preferred playstyle.</p><p><strong>Build your Shrine</strong></p><p>Some still cling to the original faith. From a tiny cult, expand your influence and excavate further into the ruins. As you expand your shrine and followers, new secrets, rewards, and <a title="Genres > Horror [722 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/horror">horror</a>s come to light.</p><p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ul><li><a title="Companies > Experience [212 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/experience">Experience</a> smooth, satisfying movement and tight controls.</li><li>Explore atmospheric, hand-drawn biomes, from the star-scorched Surface to the biomechanical Abandoned Expedition.</li><li>Fight over 70 enemies and 10 formidable bosses.</li><li>Customize your playstyle with over 30 active and passive Artifacts.</li><li>Expand your shrine to discover new treasures, abilities, and secrets.</li><li>Enjoy a rich, foreboding score by <em>Neverinth</em> and <em><a title="Games > Vigil: The Longest Night [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/vigil-the-longest-night">Vigil: The Longest Night</a></em> composer Jouni Valjakka.</li></ul></blockquote></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/10/voidwrought-coming-to-ps5-xbox-series-in-2026]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Romance of the Three Kingdoms 8 Remake with Power-Up Kit announced for PS5, PS4, Switch, and PC]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/10/romance-of-the-three-kingdoms-8-remake-with-power-up-kit-announced-for-ps5-ps4-switch-and-pc</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/romance-of-the-three-kingdoms-8-remake-with-power-up-kit-announced-for-ps5-ps4-switch-and-pc.1319596/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PS4</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Due out on January 29, 2026 in Japan.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Koei Tecmo Games [3,098 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/koei-tecmo-games">Koei Tecmo</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Kou Shibusawa [95 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/koei-tecmo-games/kou-shibusawa">Kou Shibusawa</a> have announced <em><a title="Games > Romance of the Three Kingdoms 8 Remake with Power-Up Kit" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/romance-of-the-three-kingdoms-8-remake-with-power-up-kit">Romance of the Three Kingdoms 8 Remake with Power-Up Kit</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,573 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,422 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,802 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [24,483 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a>, the latest issue of Weekly Famitsu reveals. It will launch on January 29, 2026 in Japan. The console versions will cost 10,780 yen, while the “Power-Up Kit” can be purchased as a standalone upgrade to <em><a title="Games > Romance of the Three Kingdoms 8 Remake [7 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/romance-of-the-three-kingdoms-8-remake">Romance of the Three Kingdoms 8 Remake</a></em> for 4,730 yen. <span id="more-998725"></span></p><p><em>Romance of the Three Kingdoms 8 Remake with Power-Up Kit</em> introduces the following content:</p><ul><li>New Systems<ul><li>Gems – Unlock them to enhance your abilities.</li><li>Turning Points – Build up over time and occur randomly, and have a dramatic effect that can completely reverse the situation.</li></ul></li><li>Five additional fictional scenarios</li><li>Additional Traits</li><li>User interface improvements</li><li>Significantly improved combat with enhanced tempo</li><li>Algorithm revisions</li><li>A total of over 1,000 officers</li><li>A total of 55 scenarios across all starting years</li><li>Chinese voice-overs</li></ul><p>Thanks, <a href="https://ryokutya2089.com/archives/91517" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ryokutya2089</a>.</p><!-- AD: content -->
        </div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/10/romance-of-the-three-kingdoms-8-remake-with-power-up-kit-announced-for-ps5-ps4-switch-and-pc]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
